SELECT sensor_data.device_id,
    sensor_data.location,
    sensor_data.temperature,
    sensor_data.humidity,
    sensor_data.pressure,
    sensor_data."time"
   FROM sensor_data
  WHERE (sensor_data."time" > (now() - '01:00:00'::interval))
  ORDER BY sensor_data."time" DESC;

customProperties.view_definition:
SELECT h.hour,
    h.location,
    h.avg_temperature,
    h.avg_humidity,
    h.sample_count,
        CASE
            WHEN (h.avg_temperature > (25)::double precision) THEN 'Hot'::text
            WHEN (h.avg_temperature < (15)::double precision) THEN 'Cold'::text
            ELSE 'Moderate'::text
        END AS temp_category
   FROM sensor_hourly_avg h
  WHERE (h.hour > (now() - '24:00:00'::interval));

SELECT
  h.hour,
  h.location,
  h.avg_temperature,
  h.avg_humidity,
  h.sample_count,
  CASE
    WHEN (
      h.avg_temperature > CAST((
        25
      ) AS DOUBLE PRECISION)
    )
    THEN CAST('Hot' AS TEXT)
    WHEN (
      h.avg_temperature < CAST((
        15
      ) AS DOUBLE PRECISION)
    )
    THEN CAST('Cold' AS TEXT)
    ELSE CAST('Moderate' AS TEXT)
  END AS temp_category
FROM sensor_hourly_avg AS h
WHERE
  (
    h.hour > (
      CURRENT_TIMESTAMP - CAST('24:00:00' AS INTERVAL)
    )
  )

SELECT
  j.job_id,
  j.application_name,
  j.proc_name,
  j.schedule_interval,
  j.scheduled,
  j.config,
  js.last_run_started_at,
  js.last_successful_finish
FROM (
  timescaledb_information.jobs AS j
    LEFT JOIN timescaledb_information.job_stats AS js
      ON (
        (
          j.job_id = js.job_id
        )
      )
)
ORDER BY
  j.job_id
